{"tid":1469771,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"示威活動並不會阻止航班升降，唔好墮入政府毒計","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:04:10.000Z","uid":288270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"60999e91a06a710edb1ea2082737a48d875d81a5","tid":1469771,"uid":288270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:59:34.000Z","msg":"8月12及13日機場示威者非常理性，當然示威人士眾多會造成擠塞，但並不會阻止遊客前進。我覺得政府停飛飛機完全無必要，目的賊裝嫁禍，令遊客造成不便而怪責示威者，大家千萬不要因為停飛而沾沾自喜，反而應該要提高警覺唔好墮入政府圈套，比着係你，花費不菲嘅金錢及時間嘅旅程泡湯，你係做遊客都會唔高興，有機會一定要同遊客解釋停機場係政府決定，解釋示威活動並不會阻止航班升降，唔好墮入政府毒計。"},{"pid":"04c1d003fcc0b6a445277227ef4f8e99f0230fcc","tid":1469771,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:03:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f9cbbed0a0ab477b281c1785facaac5c9ba089","tid":1469771,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:04:10.000Z","msg":"［前機場職員話你知 x 勸世文] 驕 兵 必 敗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468780</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}